data.description:
This is the perfect family home! So much space for a growing family! Large living room that opens into the formal dining room. There is also a large kitchen with a breakfast nook. 4 large bedrooms and 2.5 baths. This home also features an inviting backyard that backs up to the woods! This one checks all the boxes!

This home qualifies for 100% financing option with the PATH loan at United Community Bank.
